  ('dietitian-moex-04384', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-113-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '甲君在炎熱的夏日爬山，下列何種狀況不合理？', '["發生熱衰竭時，會昏倒且體溫稍微增加", "臉部潮紅且大量流汗，會造成血壓上升", "散熱隨著運動反射性增加，體溫穩定", "體溫持續上升但不出汗，會發生熱休克"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:35+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "67543ae9d102", "answer_pdf_sha1": "59e7cd37c769", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "101", "s": "0103", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 14, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-04385', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-113-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '戰鬥或逃跑（fight-or-flight）反應及運動時，都會增加交感神經活性。此時對腎臟的影響，下列敘述何 者正確？', '["入球小動脈（afferent arteriole）舒張", "腎絲球過濾速率（glomerular filtration rate）下降", "增加尿液生成量", "出球小動脈（efferent arteriole）收縮"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:35+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "67543ae9d102", "answer_pdf_sha1": "59e7cd37c769", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "101", "s": "0103", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 15, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
