  ('dietitian-moex-04387', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-113-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '腎絲球過濾液之體積，會因大部分的鹽分及水分再吸收回血液循環而持續下降，而由腎絲球囊（glomerular capsule）過濾至近曲小管之濾液，其滲透壓大約為何？', '["200 mOsm", "300 mOsm", "400 mOsm", "500 mOsm"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:35+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "67543ae9d102", "answer_pdf_sha1": "59e7cd37c769", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "101", "s": "0103", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 17, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-04388', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-113-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於賽氏細胞（Sertoli cells）的敘述，下列何者正確？', '["受黃體生成素（luteinizing hormone）調控刺激精子生成", "受濾泡刺激素（follicle-stimulating hormone）調控生成雌激素（estrogen）", "負責分泌睪固酮（testosterone）", "形成細胞屏障，滋養發育中精子"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:35+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "67543ae9d102", "answer_pdf_sha1": "59e7cd37c769", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "101", "s": "0103", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 18, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
