  ('dietitian-moex-04390', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-113-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何種賀爾蒙的作用為促進骨蝕作用（bone resorption）及血鈣增加？', '["降血鈣素（calcitonin）", "生長激素（growth hormone）", "副甲狀腺素（parathyroid hormone）", "骨化三醇（1, 25-dihydroxyvitamin D ） 3"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:35+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "67543ae9d102", "answer_pdf_sha1": "59e7cd37c769", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "101", "s": "0103", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 20, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-04391', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-113-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於細胞介導免疫系統（cell-mediated immunity）的敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["主要是靠抗體防禦入侵至血液和淋巴中的外來抗原", "此系統主要是攻擊病原體感染的細胞或腫瘤細胞", "細胞毒性T細胞（cytotoxic T cells）參與此機制", "輔助T細胞（helper T cells）間接參與此機制"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:35+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "67543ae9d102", "answer_pdf_sha1": "59e7cd37c769", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "101", "s": "0103", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 21, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-04392', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-113-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於壓力感應反射（baroreceptor reflex）的敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["壓力感受器（baroreceptor）主要位於主動脈體（aortic body）及頸動脈體（carotid body）", "壓力感受器（baroreceptor）的感覺神經纖維動作電位頻率隨著動脈血壓上升而增加", "壓力感受器（baroreceptor）的感覺神經活動通過迷走神經（vagus nerve）和舌咽神經 （glossopharyngeal nerve）傳到延髓", "壓力感應反射是藉由交感和副交感神經支配心臟和血管調節血壓"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:35+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "67543ae9d102", "answer_pdf_sha1": "59e7cd37c769", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "101", "s": "0103", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 22, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('dietitian-moex-04393', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-113-629fe76c', 'sub-dietitian-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '李先生的動脈收縮壓是120 mmHg，動脈舒張壓是90 mmHg，心搏出量（stroke volume）是80 mL，心律是60 bpm，其總周邊阻力（total peripheral resistance）最接近下列何者？', '["10 mmHg×min/L", "20 mmHg×min/L", "30 mmHg×min/L", "40 mmHg×min/L"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:35+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "67543ae9d102", "answer_pdf_sha1": "59e7cd37c769", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "113100", "c": "101", "s": "0103", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "生理學與生物化學", "year": "113", "exam_name": "113年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、113年專技人員高等考試心理師、法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛...", "original_question_number": 23, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL)
